text: Howard Bagguley (born 31 May 1909, date of death unknown) was a Canadian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Canadian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Canada Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa
